  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/GSS\/GSS_S_CRED_UNAVAIL\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T15:43:10Z\n---\n\n# GSS_S_CRED_UNAVAIL\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nUnavailable credential.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar GSS_S_CRED_UNAVAIL: UInt { get }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThis value is currently an alias of the generic [doc:\/\/com.apple.gss\/documentation\/GSS\/GSS_S_FAILURE].\n\n## Routine Errors\n\n- **GSS_S_BAD_MECH**: Unsupported mechanism.\n- **GSS_S_BAD_NAME**: Invalid name.\n- **GSS_S_BAD_NAMETYPE**: Unsupported name type.\n- **GSS_S_BAD_MIC**: Failed token integrity check.\n- **GSS_S_BAD_SIG**: Failed token integrity check.\n- **GSS_S_BAD_STATUS**: Invalid status selector.\n- **GSS_S_BAD_BINDINGS**: Channel bindings mismatch.\n- **GSS_S_NO_CRED**: No valid credentials.\n- **GSS_S_NO_CONTEXT**: No valid security context.\n- **GSS_S_DEFECTIVE_TOKEN**: Defective token.\n- **GSS_S_DEFECTIVE_CREDENTIAL**: Defective credential.\n- **GSS_S_CREDENTIALS_EXPIRED**: Expired credential.\n- **GSS_S_CONTEXT_EXPIRED**: Expired context.\n- **GSS_S_FAILURE**: An unspecified error.\n- **GSS_S_BAD_QOP**: Unsupported QOP value.\n\n",
